9/* Effective dimension-6 operators describing four-fermion operators involved in
10* tt production at hadron colliders. Such basis is described in 1807.02121
11*/
12
13#include "NPSMEFT6dtopquark.h"
14#include <limits>
15#include <gsl/gsl_sf.h>
16#include "std_make_vector.h"

19const std::string NPSMEFT6dtopquark::NPSMEFT6dtopquarkVars[NNPSMEFT6dtopquarkVars]
20 = {"C_phit","C_phiQ3","C_phiQ1","C_phiQm","C_tW",
21 "C_tZ","C_tB","C_tphi","C_phib","C_bW","C_bB","C_bZ",
22 "C_phitb","C_tG","C_ed","C_eq","C_ld","C_lqP","C_eu",
23 "C_lu","C_lqM","C_tu8","C_td8", "C_Qq18","C_tq8",
24 "C_Qq38","C_Qu8","C_Qd8","C_Qd1","C_Qu1","C_td1",
25 "C_tu1","C_tq1","C_Qq11","C_Qq31"
26 //Operators for CPV study in tth and thj
27 ,"C_phiG","C_phiGtil","C_phiW","C_phiWtil",
28 "C_tphiIm","C_tGIm","C_tWIm","C_tBIm","C_tZIm"
29 };

193
194// Flag to swith on/off the quadratic terms. flag = true means quadratic terms
195//are switched on
196
197bool NPSMEFT6dtopquark::setFlag(const std::string name, const bool value)
198{
199 bool res = false;
200 if(name.compare("Quadraticflag") == 0) {
201 std::cout<<"Quadraticflag = "<< value <<std::endl;
202 flag_Quadratic = value;
203 res = true;
204 }
205 else if(name.compare("flag_LHC_WG_Basis") == 0) {
206 std::cout<<"flag_LHC_WG_Basis = "<< value <<std::endl;
207 flag_LHC_WG_Basis = value;
208 res = true;
209 }
210 else
211 res = StandardModel::setFlag(name,value);
212
213 return(res);
214}

232FB_asymmetry_Tevatron_tt_diff_mtt_NPSMEFT6dtopquark::FB_asymmetry_Tevatron_tt_diff_mtt_NPSMEFT6dtopquark(const StandardModel& SM_i)
233: ThObservable(SM_i),myNPSMEFT6dtopquark(static_cast<const NPSMEFT6dtopquark&> (SM_i))
234{
235
236 setParametersForObservable(make_vector<std::string>()
237 << "SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450" << "SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450"
238 << "SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550" << "SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550"
239 << "SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650" << "SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650"
240 << "SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_650_750" << "SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750");
241
242
243}
244
245
246double FB_asymmetry_Tevatron_tt_diff_mtt_NPSMEFT6dtopquark::computeThValue()
247{
248
249 b_min = getBinMin();
250 b_max = getBinMax();
251
252 bool flag_Quadratic= false; //Needs to be properly defined
253
254
255
256
257 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
258 double C_Qd8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qd8();
259 double C_Qd1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qd1();
260 double C_Qu1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qu1();
261 double C_Qu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qu8();
262 double C_td1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_td1();
263 double C_td8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_td8();
264 double C_tq1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq1();
265 double C_tq8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq8();
266 double C_tu1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tu1();
267 double C_tu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tu8();
268 double C_Qq11 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq11();
269 double C_Qq31 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq31();
270 double C_Qq18 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq18();
271 double C_Qq38 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq38();
272
273
274
275 if(b_min == 350 && b_max == 450){
276
277
278 double SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450");
279 double SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450");
280 double SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_350_450 = SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450*SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450;
281
282 double SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_350_450+SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450);
283 double SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450-SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_350_450);
284
285
286 if(flag_Quadratic){
287
288 return 0.;
289
290 }
291 else{
292
293
294
295 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_madgraph = 1.708900;
296 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_NP = 0.014331*C_Qq11+0.020387*C_Qq31+0.057020*C_Qq38+
297 0.008985*C_Qu1+0.075826*C_Qu8+-0.005241*C_td1+0.013312*C_td8+0.011673*C_tq1+0.075137*C_tu8+
298 -0.000215*C_Qd1+0.015275*C_Qd8+0.089885*C_Qq18+0.461893*C_tG+0.088284*C_tq8+0.011721*C_tu1;
299 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_madgraph = 1.711870;
300 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_NP = 0.015137*C_Qq11+0.020418*C_Qq31+0.061615*C_Qq38+
301 0.005954*C_Qu1+0.072189*C_Qu8+0.002100*C_td1+0.015387*C_td8+0.011721*C_tq1+0.072523*C_tu8+
302 -0.000797*C_Qd1+0.013454*C_Qd8+0.088964*C_Qq18+0.457535*C_tG+0.090719*C_tq8+0.008783*C_tu1;
303
304 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450*sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_NP/sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_madgraph;
305 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450*sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_NP/sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_madgraph;
306
307 double NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_350_450 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_NP_Corrected - sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_NP_Corrected;
308 double NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_350_450_NP_Corrected + sigma_neg_bin_mtt_350_450_NP_Corrected;;
309
310 //return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450*(1+(NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_350_450-NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450)/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450);
311
312 return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450 + (NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_350_450
313 - SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_350_450*NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450
314 )/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_350_450;
315
316
317 }
318
319 } else if(b_min == 450 && b_max == 550){
320
321
322 double SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550");
323 double SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550");
324 double SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_450_550 = SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550*SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550;
325
326 double SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_450_550+SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550);
327 double SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550-SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_450_550);
328
329
330 if(flag_Quadratic){
331
332 return 0.;
333
334 }
335 else{
336
337
338
339 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_madgraph = 0.700156;
340 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_NP = 0.000293*C_Qd1+0.006654*C_Qd8+0.056437*C_Qq18+
341 0.202154*C_tG+0.057218*C_tq8+0.005943*C_tu1+0.012571*C_Qq11+0.014036*C_Qq31+0.041744*C_Qq38+
342 0.004409*C_Qu1+0.048109*C_Qu8+-0.000686*C_td1+0.007816*C_td8+0.005690*C_tq1+0.048751*C_tu8;
343 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_madgraph = 0.697721;
344 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_NP = +-0.000320*C_Qd1+0.008928*C_Qd8+0.056860*C_Qq18+
345 0.200120*C_tG+0.055877*C_tq8+0.008468*C_tu1+0.010415*C_Qq11+0.015990*C_Qq31+0.039785*C_Qq38+
346 0.004021*C_Qu1+0.049076*C_Qu8+0.000080*C_td1+0.007790*C_td8+0.007160*C_tq1+0.048573*C_tu8;
347
348 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550*sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_NP/sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_madgraph;
349 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550*sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_NP/sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_madgraph;
350
351 double NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_450_550 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_NP_Corrected - sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_NP_Corrected;
352 double NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_450_550_NP_Corrected + sigma_neg_bin_mtt_450_550_NP_Corrected;;
353
354 //return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550*(1+(NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_450_550-NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550)/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550);
355
356
357 return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550 + (NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_450_550
358 - SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_450_550*NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550
359 )/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_450_550;
360
361
362 }
363
364 } else if(b_min == 550 && b_max == 650){
365
366
367 double SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650");
368 double SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650");
369 double SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650 = SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650*SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650;
370
371 double SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650+SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650);
372 double SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650-SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650);
373
374
375 if(flag_Quadratic){
376
377 return 0.;
378
379 }
380 else{
381
382
383
384 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_madgraph = 0.225585;
385 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP = 0.005195*C_Qq11+0.007938*C_Qq31+0.020820*C_Qq38+
386 0.001724*C_Qu1+0.024030*C_Qu8+-0.000224*C_td1+0.003242*C_td8+0.002375*C_tq1+0.023554*C_tu8+
387 0.000035*C_Qd1+0.003262*C_Qd8+0.026734*C_Qq18+0.068150*C_tG+0.027216*C_tq8+0.003859*C_tu1;
388 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_madgraph = 0.226014;
389 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP = 0.007480*C_Qq11+0.008103*C_Qq31+0.020939*C_Qq38+
390 0.001998*C_Qu1+0.023779*C_Qu8+-0.000302*C_td1+0.003158*C_td8+0.002697*C_tq1+0.024310*C_tu8+
391 -0.000427*C_Qd1+0.003031*C_Qd8+0.027516*C_Qq18+0.069044*C_tG+0.026921*C_tq8+0.003865*C_tu1;
392
393 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650*sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP/sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_madgraph;
394 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650*sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP/sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_madgraph;
395
396 double NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected - sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected;
397 double NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected + sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected;;
398
399 //return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650*(1+(NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650-NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650)/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650);
400
401 return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650 + (NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650

430 0.001106*C_Qu1+0.018423*C_Qu8+-0.000255*C_td1+0.001826*C_td8+0.001752*C_tq1+0.018350*C_tu8;
431 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_madgraph = 0.104541;

442 //return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_650_750*(1+(NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_650_750-NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750)/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750);

499 else{

564double sigmattbarTev::computeThValue()
565{
566
567 double SM_ttbar_tev = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_ttbar_tev");
568 double xttbarTev_madgraph_LO = 4948.8;//fb
569
570 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
571 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
572 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
573 double mC_tu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tu8();
574 double mC_td8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_td8();
575 double C_Qq18 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq18();
576 double C_tq8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq8();
577 double C_Qq38 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq38();
578 double C_Qu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qu8();
579 double C_Qd8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qd8();
580
581
582 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
583 if(flag_Quadratic){
584 return SM_ttbar_tev + (0.303*mC_tu8+ 0.051*mC_td8 +1.378*C_tG + 0.022*mC_tu8*mC_tu8+ 0.004*mC_td8*mC_td8+0.123*C_tG*C_tG + 0.381130*C_Qq18 + 0.380930*C_tq8 + 0.271890*C_Qq38 + 0.326390*C_Qu8 + 0.054694*C_Qd8)*(1000*SM_ttbar_tev/xttbarTev_madgraph_LO);
585 }
586 else{
587 return SM_ttbar_tev + (0.303*mC_tu8+ 0.051*mC_td8 +1.378*C_tG + 0.381130*C_Qq18 + 0.380930*C_tq8 + 0.271890*C_Qq38 + 0.326390*C_Qu8 + 0.054694*C_Qd8)*(1000*SM_ttbar_tev/xttbarTev_madgraph_LO);
588 }
589 }
590 else{
591 if(flag_Quadratic){
592 return SM_ttbar_tev + (0.303*mC_tu8+ 0.051*mC_td8 +1.378*C_tG + 0.022*mC_tu8*mC_tu8+ 0.004*mC_td8*mC_td8+0.123*C_tG*C_tG)*(1000*SM_ttbar_tev/xttbarTev_madgraph_LO);
593 }
594 else{
595 return SM_ttbar_tev + (0.303*mC_tu8+ 0.051*mC_td8 +1.378*C_tG )*(1000*SM_ttbar_tev/xttbarTev_madgraph_LO);
596 }
597 }

636 +0.04789*C_tW*C_tW+0.00268*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3+0.00758*C_tG*C_tG+0.02019*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))+0.0006*(-C_phitb/(0.998))*(-C_phitb/(0.998)))*(1000*SM_sigmaschannelTev/xschan_madgraph_LO) ;
637 }

640 }

769 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650*sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP/sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_madgraph;
770
771 double NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected - sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected;
772 double NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected + sigma_neg_bin_mtt_550_650_NP_Corrected;;
773
774 return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_550_650*(1+(NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_550_650-NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650)/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_550_650);
775
776 }
777
778 } else if(b_min == 650 && b_max == 750){
779
780
781 double SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_650_750 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_650_750");
782 double SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750");
783 double SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_650_750 = SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_650_750*SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750;
784
785 double SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_650_750+SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750);
786 double SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750 =0.5*(SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750-SM_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_650_750);
787
788
789 if(flag_Quadratic){
790
791 return 0.;
792
793 }
794 else{
795
796
797
798 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_madgraph = 0.097727;
799 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_NP = 0.;
800 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_madgraph = 0.097766;
801 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_NP = 0.;
802
803 double sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750*sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_NP/sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_madgraph;
804 double sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_NP_Corrected = SM_sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750*sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_NP/sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_madgraph;
805
806 double NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_650_750 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_NP_Corrected - sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_NP_Corrected;
807 double NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750 = sigma_pos_bin_mtt_650_750_NP_Corrected + sigma_neg_bin_mtt_650_750_NP_Corrected;;
808
809 return SM_FB_asymmetry_bin_mtt_650_750*(1+(NP_FB_asymmetry_num_bin_mtt_650_750-NP_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750)/SM_FB_asymmetry_deno_bin_mtt_650_750);
810
811 }
812
813 } else {
814 throw std::runtime_error("\nERROR: Please specify a correct binning range for FB_asymmetry_Tevatron_tt_diff_mtt_LO.\n");
815 }
816
817
818}

845
846double F0::computeThValue()
847{
848 double F0_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("F0_SM");
849 double F0_madgraph = 0.70381;
850 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
851 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
852 double C_tW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tW();
853 double C_bW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bW();
854
855
856 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
857 if(flag_Quadratic){
858 return F0_SM + (-0.0569231*C_tW + 0.0022956*C_tW*C_tW -
859 0.00215306*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))
860 )*(F0_SM/F0_madgraph);
861 }
862 else{
863 return F0_SM + (-0.0569231*(C_tW) )*(F0_SM/F0_madgraph);
864 }
865 }
866
867 else{
868 if(flag_Quadratic){
869 return F0_SM + (-0.0569231*C_tW + 0.0022956*C_tW*C_tW -
870 0.00215306*((C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)))*((C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)))
871 )*(F0_SM/F0_madgraph);
872 }
873 else{
874 return F0_SM + (-0.0569231*(C_tW) )*(F0_SM/F0_madgraph);
875 }
876 }
877}

886double FL::computeThValue()
887{
888 double FL_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("FL_SM");
889 double FL_madgraph = 0.29619;
890 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
891 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
892
893 double C_tW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tW();
894 double C_bW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bW();
895 double C_phitb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phitb();
896
897 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
898 if(flag_Quadratic){
899 return FL_SM + ( 0.0569227*C_tW - 0.0022956*C_tW*C_tW
900 - 0.0011115*((C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)))*((C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)))
901 - 0.000105115*((-C_phitb/(0.998)))*((-C_phitb/(0.998)))
902 )*(FL_SM/FL_madgraph);
903 }
904 else{
905 return FL_SM + (0.0569227*(C_tW) )*(FL_SM/FL_madgraph);
906 }
907 }
908
909 else{
910 if(flag_Quadratic){
911 return FL_SM + ( 0.0569227*C_tW - 0.0022956*C_tW*C_tW
912 - 0.0011115*((C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)))*((C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)))
913 - 0.000105115*((-C_phitb/(0.998)))*((-C_phitb/(0.998)))
914 )*(FL_SM/FL_madgraph);
915 }
916 else{
917 return FL_SM + (0.0569227*(C_tW) )*(FL_SM/FL_madgraph);
918 }
919 }
920

1032{

1040 double C_td8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_td8();
1041 double C_Qd8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qd8();
1042 double C_Qu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qu8();
1043 double C_tq8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq8();
1044 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
1045 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
1046 double C_phit = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phit();
1047 double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
1048 double C_phiQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
1049 double C_phiQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();

1051 double C_tZ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tZ();
1052 double C_tB = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tB();
1053 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
1054
1055
1056
1057 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
1058 if(flag_Quadratic) {
1059 return SM_ttZ_inc+ (-3.25*C_tZ+ 288.50*C_tG + 48.59*C_phit -76.50*C_phiQm

1061 +3.75*C_phiQm*C_phiQm-0.0016*C_phit*C_phiQm)*(SM_ttZ_inc/(xttzNLO_madgraph))

1063
1064 }
1065 else{
1066 return SM_ttZ_inc + (-3.25*C_tZ+288.50*C_tG+48.59*C_phit
1067 -76.50*C_phiQm)*(SM_ttZ_inc/(xttzNLO_madgraph))+
1068 (-0.017852*C_Qq38+0.011527*C_tu8+0.067759*C_Qq18+0.009777*C_td8+0.015271*C_Qd8+0.017474*C_Qu8+0.055888*C_tq8+0.002146*C_phiQ3)*(1000*SM_ttZ_inc/xttzLO_madgraph);
1069 }
1070 }
1071 else{

1073 return SM_ttZ_inc+ (-3.25*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW)+ 288.50*C_tG + 48.59*C_phit -76.50*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3)
1074 + 62.33*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW)*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW)+ 291.80*C_tG*C_tG +3.20*C_phit*C_phit
1075 +3.75*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3)*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3)-0.0016*C_phit*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3))*(SM_ttZ_inc/(xttzNLO_madgraph))
1076 +(-0.017852*C_Qq38+0.031201*C_Qq38*C_Qq38+0.011527*C_tu8+0.005967*C_tu8*C_tu8+0.067759*C_Qq18+0.031474*C_Qq18*C_Qq18+0.009777*C_td8+0.003648*C_td8*C_td8+0.015271*C_Qd8+0.007609*C_Qd8*C_Qd8+0.017474*C_Qu8+0.011569*C_Qu8*C_Qu8+0.055888*C_tq8+0.021441*C_tq8*C_tq8)*(1000*SM_ttZ_inc/xttzLO_madgraph);
1077 }
1078 else{
1079 return SM_ttZ_inc + (-3.25*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW)+288.50*C_tG+48.59*C_phit
1080 -76.50*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3))*(SM_ttZ_inc/(xttzNLO_madgraph))+
1081 (-0.017852*C_Qq38+0.011527*C_tu8+0.067759*C_Qq18+0.009777*C_td8+0.015271*C_Qd8+0.017474*C_Qu8+0.055888*C_tq8+0.002146*C_phiQ3)*(1000*SM_ttZ_inc/xttzLO_madgraph);

1146double sigmattW::computeThValue()
1147{

1149 double NLOxttw_madgraph = 543.3;//fb
1150 double LOxttw_madgraph = 407.2;//fb
1151 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
1152 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();

1155 double C_Qq38 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq38();
1156 double C_tq8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq8();
1157

1159
1160 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){

1162 return SM_ttW_inc + (158.3*C_tG + 23.4*C_tG*C_tG)*(SM_ttW_inc/NLOxttw_madgraph)+
1163 (119.3*C_Qq18 + 42.0*C_Qq18*C_Qq18 - 43.7*C_Qq38 + 95.8*C_Qq38*C_Qq38 + 119.4*C_tq8 + 42.1*C_tq8*C_tq8 - 31.9*C_Qq18*C_Qq38 + 7.1*C_Qq18*C_tq8 - 3.4*C_Qq38*C_tq8 )*(SM_ttW_inc/LOxttw_madgraph);
1164 }
1165 else{
1166 return (SM_ttW_inc + (158.3*C_tG)*(SM_ttW_inc/NLOxttw_madgraph))+
1167 (119.3*C_Qq18 - 43.7*C_Qq38 + 119.4*C_tq8 )*(SM_ttW_inc/LOxttw_madgraph);
1168 }
1169 }
1170
1171 else{
1172 if(flag_Quadratic){
1173 return (SM_ttW_inc + (158.3*C_tG + 23.4*C_tG*C_tG)*(SM_ttW_inc/NLOxttw_madgraph))+
1174 (119.3*C_Qq18 + 42.0*C_Qq18*C_Qq18 - 43.7*C_Qq38 + 95.8*C_Qq38*C_Qq38 + 119.4*C_tq8 + 42.1*C_tq8*C_tq8 - 31.9*C_Qq18*C_Qq38 + 7.1*C_Qq18*C_tq8 - 3.4*C_Qq38*C_tq8 )*(SM_ttW_inc/LOxttw_madgraph);
1175 }
1176 else{
1177 return (SM_ttW_inc + (158.3*C_tG)*(SM_ttW_inc/NLOxttw_madgraph))+
1178 (119.3*C_Qq18 - 43.7*C_Qq38 + 119.4*C_tq8 )*(SM_ttW_inc/LOxttw_madgraph);

1426 + 1.30178*C_tG + 0.129086*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532)) + 0.0143561*(-C_phitb/(0.998))*(-C_phitb/(0.998)) -0.0175843*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(-C_phitb/(0.998)))*(SM_tW_inc_8TeV/NLOxgbtw_madgraph_8TeV) ;

1471

1478 + 15.3*C_tZ*C_tZ + 80.0*C_tW*C_tW + 25.439*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3
1479 + 1.23048*C_phiQm*C_phiQm + 0.492986*C_phit*C_phit + 5.4*C_tG*C_tG
1480 + 48.7*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))+3.4*(-C_phitb/(0.998))*(-C_phitb/(0.998))
1481 + 4.19554*C_phiQ3*C_phiQm -0.531018*C_phiQ3*C_phit -0.818108*C_phiQm*C_phit-1.1*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(-C_phitb/(0.998))
1482 )*(SM_tZQ_inc/xztq_NLO_madgraph);
1483 }
1484 else{
1485 return SM_tZQ_inc +(-5.9*C_tZ + 22.2*C_tW + 176.075*C_phiQ3 +

1487 }
1488 }
1489
1490 else{
1491 if(flag_Quadratic){
1492 return SM_tZQ_inc +(-5.9*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW) + 22.2*C_tW + 176.075*C_phiQ3 +

1494 + 15.3*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW)*(-0.472123*C_tB + 0.881533*C_tW) + 80.0*C_tW*C_tW + 25.439*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3
1495 + 1.23048*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3)*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3) + 0.492986*C_phit*C_phit + 5.4*C_tG*C_tG
1496 + 48.7*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))*(C_bW/(0.999*0.6532))+3.4*(-C_phitb/(0.998))*(-C_phitb/(0.998))

1500 else{

1502 17.9006*(C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3) + 4.66561*C_phit - 3.9*C_tG)*(SM_tZQ_inc/xztq_NLO_madgraph);

1570tH_tchan::tH_tchan(const StandardModel& SM_i)
1571: ThObservable(SM_i),myNPSMEFT6dtopquark(static_cast<const NPSMEFT6dtopquark&> (SM_i))
1572{
1573 setParametersForObservable(make_vector<std::string>() << "SM_tH_tchan_value" );
1574}
1575
1576double tH_tchan::computeThValue()
1577{
1578 double SM_tH_tchan_value = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_tH_tchan_value");
1579 double C_tW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tW();
1580 double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
1581 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
1582 double C_tphi = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tphi();
1583 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
1584 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
1585 double NLO_madgraph = 71.18;//fb
1586 double upper_lim = 8*SM_tH_tchan_value;
1587
1588 //We introduce the ratio Th/Exp to take into account the upper limit
1589 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
1590 if(flag_Quadratic){
1591 double cross_sect = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi+56.1*C_tW*C_tW+13.4*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3-1.3*C_tG*C_tG+0.8*C_tphi*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/NLO_madgraph);
1592 return cross_sect/upper_lim;
1593 }
1594 else{
1595 double cross_sect = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/NLO_madgraph);
1596 return cross_sect/upper_lim;
1597 }
1598 }
1599
1600 else{
1601 if(flag_Quadratic){
1602 double cross_sect = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi+56.1*C_tW*C_tW+13.4*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3-1.3*C_tG*C_tG+0.8*C_tphi*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/NLO_madgraph);
1603 return cross_sect/upper_lim;
1604 }
1605 else{
1606 double cross_sect = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/NLO_madgraph);
1607 return cross_sect/upper_lim;
1608 }
1609 }

1634 //double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
1635 //double C_bW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bW();

1648 (0.0203*mC_tu8+0.0126*mC_td8+0.0088*mC_tu8*mC_tu8+0.0046*mC_td8*mC_td8 + 0.038028*C_Qq18 + 0.03802*C_tq8 + 0.009163*C_Qq38 + 0.023543*C_Qu8 + 0.014638*C_Qd8)*(1000*SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_LO) ;

1669ttHSUM::ttHSUM(const StandardModel& SM_i)

1674
1675double ttHSUM::computeThValue()
1676{
1677
1678 double SM_ttH_inc = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_ttH_inc");
1679 double SM_tH_tchan_value = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_tH_tchan_value");
1680
1681 double xtth_madgraph_NLO = 459.7;//fb
1682// double xtth_madgraph_LO = 354.57;//fb //with dinamical scale
1683 double xtth_madgraph_LO = 459;//fb //with fixed scale
1684 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
1685 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
1686 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
1687 double C_tW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tW();
1688 double C_tphi = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tphi();
1689 double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
1690 double C_bW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bW();
1691 double C_phitb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phitb();
1692 double mC_tu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tu8();
1693 double mC_td8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_td8();
1694 double C_Qq18 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq18();
1695 double C_tq8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq8();
1696 double C_Qq38 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq38();
1697 double C_Qu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qu8();
1698 double C_Qd8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qd8();
1699
1700
1701
1702
1703 double xtH_madgraph_NLO = 71.18;//fb
1704 double xtH_madgraph_LO = 66.6;//fb
1705
1706
1707 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
1708 if(flag_Quadratic){
1709 double x_sec_ttH = SM_ttH_inc + (-59.3*C_tphi+ 458.9*C_tG +1.9*C_tphi*C_tphi+ 598.6*C_tG*C_tG)*(SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_NLO)+
1710 (0.0203*mC_tu8+0.0126*mC_td8+0.0088*mC_tu8*mC_tu8+0.0046*mC_td8*mC_td8 + 0.038028*C_Qq18 + 0.03802*C_tq8 + 0.009163*C_Qq38 + 0.023543*C_Qu8 + 0.014638*C_Qd8)*(1000*SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_LO) ;
1711
1712 double x_sec_tH = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi+56.1*C_tW*C_tW+13.4*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3-1.3*C_tG*C_tG+0.8*C_tphi*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/xtH_madgraph_NLO)+
1713 (1.9*C_bW*C_bW+0.06*C_phitb*C_phitb)*(SM_tH_tchan_value/xtH_madgraph_LO);
1714
1715 return x_sec_ttH+x_sec_tH;
1716 }
1717 else{
1718 double x_sec_tH = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/xtH_madgraph_NLO);
1719
1720 double x_sec_ttH = SM_ttH_inc + (-59.3*C_tphi+ 458.9*C_tG )*(SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_NLO)+
1721 (0.0203*mC_tu8+0.0126*mC_td8 + 0.038028*C_Qq18 + 0.03802*C_tq8 + 0.009163*C_Qq38 + 0.023543*C_Qu8 + 0.014638*C_Qd8)*(1000*SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_LO);
1722
1723 return x_sec_tH+x_sec_ttH;
1724 }
1725 }
1726
1727 else{
1728 if(flag_Quadratic){
1729
1730 double x_sec_tH = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi+56.1*C_tW*C_tW+13.4*C_phiQ3*C_phiQ3-1.3*C_tG*C_tG+0.8*C_tphi*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/xtH_madgraph_NLO)+
1731 (1.9*C_bW*C_bW+0.06*C_phitb*C_phitb)*(SM_tH_tchan_value/xtH_madgraph_LO);
1732
1733 double x_sec_ttH = SM_ttH_inc + (-59.3*C_tphi+ 458.9*C_tG +1.9*C_tphi*C_tphi+ 598.6*C_tG*C_tG)*(SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_NLO)+
1734 (0.0203*mC_tu8+0.0126*mC_td8+0.0088*mC_tu8*mC_tu8+0.0046*mC_td8*mC_td8)*(1000*SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_LO) ;
1735
1736 return x_sec_tH+x_sec_ttH;
1737 }
1738 else{
1739 double x_sec_tH = SM_tH_tchan_value + ((21.1*C_tW-8.3*C_phiQ3-0.1*C_tG-0.5*C_tphi))*(SM_tH_tchan_value/xtH_madgraph_NLO);
1740
1741 double x_sec_ttH = SM_ttH_inc + (-59.3*C_tphi+ 458.9*C_tG )*(SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_NLO)+
1742 (0.0203*mC_tu8+0.0126*mC_td8)*(1000*SM_ttH_inc/xtth_madgraph_LO);
1743
1744 return x_sec_tH+x_sec_ttH;
1745 }
1746 }

1979ttWqEM::ttWqEM(const StandardModel& SM_i)
1980: ThObservable(SM_i),myNPSMEFT6dtopquark(static_cast<const NPSMEFT6dtopquark&> (SM_i))
1981{
1982 setParametersForObservable(make_vector<std::string>() << "ttWqEM_SM" );

1984
1985double ttWqEM::computeThValue()
1986{
1987 double ttWqEM_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("ttWqEM_SM");
1988 double C_tZ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tZ();
1989 double C_tB = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tB();
1990 double C_tW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tW();
1991 double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
1992 double C_phiQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
1993 double C_phiQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();
1994 double C_phit = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phit();
1995 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
1996 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
1997 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
1998 double ttWqEM_madgraph = 47.53;
1999
2000 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){

4308 66.38*C_tq1*C_tq1 + 1.97*C_tq8 + 14.52*C_tq8*C_tq8 + 0.26*C_tu1 + 53.41*C_tu1*C_tu1 + 1.8*C_tu8 +

4315 0.26*C_tu1 + 1.8*C_tu8)*(SM_tt_bin_3500_4000/tt_bin_3500_4000_Madgraph_NLO);

5360 double C_eu = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eu();
5361 double C_lu = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lu();
5362 double C_eq = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
5363
5364
5365 //std::cout<<"\033[1;31m C_lu = \033[0m "<< C_lu << std::endl;
5366 //std::cout<<"\033[1;31m C_eq = \033[0m "<< C_eq << std::endl;
5367
5368
5369 if(b_min == 100 && b_max == 120){
5370
5371 double SM_ttll_bin_100_120 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_sigma_ttll_bin_100_120");
5372
5373 //double ttll_bin_100_120_Madgraph = 1.;//fb
5374
5375 double total;
5376
5377 if(flag_Quadratic){
5378
5379 total = SM_ttll_bin_100_120 * 1/100 * ( 100 - 4*C_lQ1 + 0.11*C_lQ1*C_lQ1 + 4*C_lQ3 + 0.11*C_lQ3*C_lQ3 - 2.6*C_eu + 0.11 *C_eu*C_eu + 1.3*C_lu + 0.11*C_lu*C_lu + 2*C_eq + 0.11*C_eq*C_eq); //Xsec mg5 included in coefficients
5380
5381 if (total < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
5382
5383 return total;
5384
5385 }
5386 else{
5387
5388 total = SM_ttll_bin_100_120 * 1/100 * ( 100 - 4*C_lQ1 + 4*C_lQ3 - 2.6*C_eu + 1.3*C_lu + 2*C_eq ); //Xsec mg5 included in coefficients
5389
5390 if (total < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
5391
5392 return total;
5393
5394 }
5395
5396 } else if(b_min == 120 && b_max == 140){
5397
5398 double SM_ttll_bin_120_140 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_sigma_ttll_bin_120_140");
5399

5401
5402 double total;
5403
5404 if(flag_Quadratic){
5405
5406 total = SM_ttll_bin_120_140 * 1/100 * ( 100 - 10*C_lQ1 + 0.5*C_lQ1*C_lQ1 + 10*C_lQ3 + 0.5*C_lQ3*C_lQ3 - 6*C_eu + 0.5 *C_eu*C_eu + 0.6*C_lu + 0.5*C_lu*C_lu + 2.3*C_eq + 0.5*C_eq*C_eq); //Xsec mg5 included in coefficients
5407
5408 if (total < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
5409
5410 return total;
5411
5412 }
5413 else{
5414
5415 total = SM_ttll_bin_120_140 * 1/100 * ( 100 - 10*C_lQ1 + 10*C_lQ3 - 6*C_eu + 0.6*C_lu + 2.3*C_eq ); //Xsec mg5 included in coefficients
5416
5417 if (total < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
5418
5419 return total;
5420 }
5421
5422 } else if(b_min == 140 && b_max == 180){
5423
5424 double SM_ttll_bin_140_180 = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_sigma_ttll_bin_140_180");
5425
5426 //double ttll_bin_140_180_Madgraph = 0.23;//fb
5427

5433
5434 if (total < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
5435
5436 return total;
5437
5438 }
5439 else{
5440
5441 total = SM_ttll_bin_140_180 * 1/100 * ( 100 - 17*C_lQ1 + 17*C_lQ3 - 11*C_eu - 2*C_lu + 1.2*C_eq ); //Xsec mg5 included in coefficients
5442
5443 if (total < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
5444
5445 return total;
5446

5448
5449 } else if(b_min == 180 && b_max == 500){

5490{
5491
5492 double entang_D_threshold_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_entang_D_threshold");
5493 double entang_D_threshold_madgraph = -0.467;//This is actually the best SM prediction
5494
5495 double C_tG = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();

5501 double C_td8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_td8();

5503 double C_tq8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tq8();
5504 double C_tu1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tu1();
5505 double C_tu8 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tu8();
5506 double C_Qq11 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq11();
5507 double C_Qq31 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq31();
5508 double C_Qq18 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq18();
5509 double C_Qq38 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_Qq38();
5510
5511
5512 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
5513 //
5514 if(flag_Quadratic){
5515 return entang_D_threshold_SM + (-0.12093*C_tG + 0.03404*C_tG*C_tG + -0.00346*C_Qd1 +
5516 0.00164*C_Qd1*C_Qd1 + 0.00294*C_Qd8 + 0.00114*C_Qd8*C_Qd8 + 0.00121*C_Qq11 +
5517 0.00156*C_Qq11*C_Qq11 + -0.00095*C_Qq31 + -0.00044*C_Qq31*C_Qq31 + 0.00534*C_Qq18 +
5518 -0.00074*C_Qq18*C_Qq18 + -0.00153*C_Qq38 + 9e-05*C_Qq38*C_Qq38 + -0.00014*C_Qu1 +
5519 0.00041*C_Qu1*C_Qu1 + -0.00156*C_Qu8 + 0.00031*C_Qu8*C_Qu8 + -0.00217*C_td1 +
5520 -0.00186*C_td1*C_td1 + 0.00669*C_td8 + 0.00143*C_td8*C_td8 + -7e-05*C_tq1 +
5521 0.00019*C_tq1*C_tq1 + 0.00393*C_tq8 + 0.00042*C_tq8*C_tq8 + -0.00413*C_tu1 +
5522 -0.00234*C_tu1*C_tu1 + 0.0036*C_tu8 + -0.00157*C_tu8*C_tu8)
5523 *entang_D_threshold_SM/entang_D_threshold_madgraph;
5524
5525 }
5526 else{
5527
5528 return entang_D_threshold_SM + (-0.12093*C_tG + -0.00346*C_Qd1 + 0.00294*C_Qd8 +
5529 0.00121*C_Qq11 + -0.00095*C_Qq31 + 0.00534*C_Qq18 + -0.00153*C_Qq38 +
5530 -0.00014*C_Qu1 + -0.00156*C_Qu8 + -0.00217*C_td1 + 0.00669*C_td8 +
5531 -7e-05*C_tq1 + 0.00393*C_tq8 + -0.00413*C_tu1 + 0.0036*C_tu8)
5532 *entang_D_threshold_SM/entang_D_threshold_madgraph;
5533
5534 }

5903
5904a_3TeV_mumu_bb::a_3TeV_mumu_bb(const StandardModel& SM_i)
5905: ThObservable(SM_i),myNPSMEFT6dtopquark(static_cast<const NPSMEFT6dtopquark&> (SM_i))
5906{
5907 setParametersForObservable(make_vector<std::string>() << "SM_a_3TeV_mumu_bb");
5908}
5909
5910double a_3TeV_mumu_bb::computeThValue()
5911{
5912
5913 //double a_250_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80 = 69.8;//in percentage//OLD
5914 //double a_250_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80 = 0.7038
5915
5916 double asym_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_a_3TeV_mumu_bb");
5917 double cHQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
5918 double cHb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phib();
5919 double ceb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
5920 double ceQ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
5921 double clb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
5922 double clqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();
5923 double clqM = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqM();
5924 double clq1 = (clqP + clqM)/2.0;
5925 double clq3 = (clqP - clqM)/2.0;
5926
5927
5928
5929
5930 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
5931 //bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
5932
5933
5934 double cHQ1;
5935 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
5936 double cHQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();
5937 cHQ1 = cHQ3 + cHQm;
5938 }
5939 else{
5940 cHQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
5941 }
5942
5943
5944 //We provide these values at linear order
5945 double SM_pos = 8.3563;
5946 double NP_pos = 543.0139*ceb + -198.5954*ceQ + -0.2080*cHb + 0.6883*cHQ1 + 0.6883*cHQ3 + -106.3333*clb + 1296.7195*clq1 + 1296.7195*clq3;
5947
5948 double SM_neg = 1.7989;
5949 double NP_neg = 91.8085*ceb + -120.4171*ceQ + 0.1100*cHb + 0.2088*cHQ1 + 0.2088*cHQ3 + 419.7807*clb + 200.8504*clq1 + 200.8504*clq3;
5950
5951 double NP_num = NP_pos-NP_neg;
5952 double NP_deno = NP_pos+NP_pos;
5953
5954 //double SM_num = SM_pos-SM_neg;
5955 double SM_deno = SM_pos+SM_neg;
5956
5957
5958 return asym_SM + (NP_num - asym_SM*NP_deno)/SM_deno;
5959
5960}

6140
6141double a_10TeV_mumu_bb::computeThValue()
6142{
6143
6144 //double a_250_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80 = 69.8;//in percentage//OLD
6145 //double a_250_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80 = 0.7038
6146
6147 double asym_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_a_10TeV_mumu_bb");
6148 double cHQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
6149 double cHb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phib();
6150 double ceb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
6151 double ceQ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
6152 double clb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
6153 double clqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();
6154 double clqM = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqM();
6155 double clq1 = (clqP + clqM)/2.0;
6156 double clq3 = (clqP - clqM)/2.0;
6157
6158
6159
6160
6161 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
6162 //bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
6163
6164
6165 double cHQ1;
6166 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
6167 double cHQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();
6168 cHQ1 = cHQ3 + cHQm;
6169 }
6170 else{
6171 cHQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
6172 }
6173
6174
6175 //We provide these values at linear order
6176 double SM_pos = 0.7513;
6177 double NP_pos = 473.5391*ceb + -198.5954*ceQ + -0.0188*cHb + 0.0618*cHQ1 +
6178 0.0618*cHQ3 + -1354.2705*clb + 1296.7195*clq1 + 1226.6425*clq3;
6179
6180 double SM_neg = 0.1617;
6181 double NP_neg = 94.9606*ceb + -120.4171*ceQ + 0.0099*cHb + 0.0188*cHQ1 +
6182 0.0188*cHQ3 + 1622.0219*clb + 200.8504*clq1 + 201.8824*clq3;
6183
6184 double NP_num = NP_pos-NP_neg;
6185 double NP_deno = NP_pos+NP_pos;
6186
6187 //double SM_num = SM_pos-SM_neg;
6188 double SM_deno = SM_pos+SM_neg;
6189
6190
6191 return asym_SM + (NP_num - asym_SM*NP_deno)/SM_deno;
6192
6193}

6692 double clqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();

6873 double asym_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_a_250_bb_eP_P30_eM_P80");

6876 double cHb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phib();
6877 double ceb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
6878 double ceQ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
6879 double clb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
6880 double clqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();
6881 double clqM = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqM();
6882 double clq1 = (clqP + clqM)/2.0;
6883 double clq3 = (clqP - clqM)/2.0;
6884
6885
6886
6887
6888 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();

8163double a_1000_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80::computeThValue()
8164{
8165
8166 //double a_1000_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80 = 67.5 ;//in percentage OLD
8167 //double a_1000_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80 = 0.6873
8168
8169 double asym_SM = SM.getOptionalParameter("SM_a_1000_bb_eP_P30_eM_M80");
8170 double cHQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
8171 double cHb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phib();
8172 double ceb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
8173 double ceQ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
8174 double clb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
8175 double clqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();
8176 double clqM = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqM();
8177 double clq1 = (clqP + clqM)/2.0;
8178 double clq3 = (clqP - clqM)/2.0;
8179
8180
8181
8182
8183 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
8184 //bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
8185
8186
8187 double cHQ1;
8188 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
8189 double cHQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();
8190 cHQ1 = cHQ3 + cHQm;
8191 }
8192 else{
8193 cHQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
8194 }
8195
8196
8197 //We provide these values at linear order
8198 double SM_pos = 151.98186;
8199 double NP_pos = 77.08833*ceb + -4.81075*ceQ + 0.24021*cHb + 14.33980*cHQ1 +
8200 14.33980*cHQ3 + 86.15264*clb + 3077.62694*clq1 + 3077.62694*clq3;
8201
8202 double SM_neg = 28.16614;
8203 double NP_neg = 11.42967*ceb + -40.31705*ceQ + 2.84019*cHb + 2.16820*cHQ1 +
8204 2.16820*cHQ3 + 649.79336*clb + 437.04306*clq1 + 437.04306*clq3;
8205
8206 double NP_num = NP_pos-NP_neg;
8207 double NP_deno = NP_pos+NP_pos;
8208
8209 //double SM_num = SM_pos-SM_neg;
8210 double SM_deno = SM_pos+SM_neg;
8211
8212
8213 return asym_SM + (NP_num - asym_SM*NP_deno)/SM_deno;
8214}

9453 double cHb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phib();
9454 double ceb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
9455 double ceQ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
9456 double clb = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
9457 double clqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();
9458 double clqM = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqM();
9459 double clq1 = (clqP + clqM)/2.0;
9460 double clq3 = (clqP - clqM)/2.0;
9461
9462
9463
9464
9465 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
9466 //bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
9467
9468
9469 double cHQ1;
9470 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
9471 double cHQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();
9472 cHQ1 = cHQ3 + cHQm;
9473 }
9474 else{
9475 cHQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
9476 }
9477
9478
9479 //We provide these values at linear order
9480 double SM_pos = 1584.5950752;
9481 double NP_pos = 573.7625397*ceb + -55.6448403*ceQ + -39.0855201*cHb + 141.2653044*cHQ1 +
9482 141.2653044*cHQ3 + 34.2530098*clb + 1452.6897692*clq1 + 1452.6897692*clq3;
9483
9484 double SM_neg = 364.0449248;
9485 double NP_neg = 80.5374604*ceb + -394.8031597*ceQ + 16.8015205*cHb + 48.0906956*cHQ1 +
9486 48.0906956*cHQ3 + 253.3409900*clb + 208.9782308*clq1 + 208.9782308*clq3;
9487
9488 double NP_num = NP_pos-NP_neg;
9489 double NP_deno = NP_pos+NP_pos;
9490
9491 //double SM_num = SM_pos-SM_neg;
9492 double SM_deno = SM_pos+SM_neg;
9493
9494
9495 return asym_SM + (NP_num - asym_SM*NP_deno)/SM_deno;
9496}

13781
13782 return lumi*eff*opt_obs_muon_30TeV_6;
13783
13784
13785 } else if(b_min == 7 && b_max == 7){
13786
13787 double opt_obs_muon_30TeV_7 = 82.65934156076267*C_phiQm + -36.97554779688711*C_phit
13788 + -4509.21767007115*C_tW + 3614.8998799890082*C_tZ

13790 + 18172430.059509046*C_lqM + 1566603.2045368692*C_eq
13791 + 2564049.7374233436*C_lu + 11483908.709193476*C_eu;
13792
13793
13794 return lumi*eff*opt_obs_muon_30TeV_7;
13795

13797 } else if(b_min == 8 && b_max == 8){
13798

13801 + -6.681327479592764e-05*CI_tW + -0.0005712903651506302*CI_tZ

13803 + 5866674.762341308*C_lu + 943905.3767505556*C_eu;

13872 double cHGtil = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiGtil();
13873 //double cHW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiW();
13874 //double cHWtil = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiWtil();
13875 double ctHRe = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tphi();
13876 double ctHIm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tphiIm();
13877 double ctGRe = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tG();
13878 double ctGIm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tGIm();
13879 double ctWRe = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tW();
13880 double ctWIm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tWIm();
13881 double ctBRe = 0.;
13882 double ctBIm = 0.;
13883
13884
13885
13886
13887 //Expressions are written in the basis of SMEFTsim
13888 //let's change to the basis of dim6top (same as
13889 //SMEFT@NLO except for the gs on CtG). These
13890 //models define the covariance derivative
13891 //with a different convention
13892
13893 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
13894 double ctZRe = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tZ();
13895 double ctZIm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tZIm();
13896 double sw2 = 0.22305;
13897 double cw2 = 1 - sw2;
13898 double tw2 = sw2/cw2;
13899 double sw = sqrt(sw2);
13900 double tw = sqrt(tw2);
13901 ctBRe = ctZRe/sw - ctWRe/tw;
13902 ctBIm = ctZIm/sw - ctWIm/tw;
13903 ctWRe = -ctWRe;
13904 ctWIm = -ctWIm;
13905 ctGRe = -ctGRe;
13906 ctGIm = -ctGIm;
13907 }
13908 else{
13909 ctBRe = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tB();
13910 ctBIm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_tBIm();

14488 ctGRe = -ctGRe;
14489 ctGIm = -ctGIm;

14903 ctBRe = ctZRe/sw - ctWRe/tw;
14904 ctBIm = ctZIm/sw - ctWIm/tw;

15469 0.0334424612581808*ctHRe*ctHRe + 2.710148441129685*ctWIm*ctWIm + 2.710423562420865*ctWRe*ctWRe +
15470 -0.0582782715491244*cHW*cHWtil + 0.0028875063300902*cHW*ctHIm + -0.0599189477103146*cHW*ctHRe +
15471 0.0324241655935762*cHW*ctWIm + -0.6418354389210809*cHW*ctWRe + -0.0082755885390069*cHWtil*ctHIm +
15472 0.0256119540036406*cHWtil*ctHRe + -0.4445427933974889*cHWtil*ctWIm + -0.0102638339471822*cHWtil*ctWRe +
15473 0.0003425431837288*ctHIm*ctHRe + 0.0736905682201566*ctHIm*ctWIm + -0.0517246077639719*ctHIm*ctWRe +
15474 0.038675770013493*ctHRe*ctWIm + 0.1210837943540063*ctHRe*ctWRe + -0.0200958660055103*ctWIm*ctWRe;
15475
15476
15477 //double num = (trip_prod_pos_Mad + trip_prod_pos_NP) - (trip_prod_neg_Mad + trip_prod_neg_NP);
15478 //double deno = (trip_prod_pos_Mad + trip_prod_pos_NP) + (trip_prod_neg_Mad + trip_prod_neg_NP);
15479
15480
15481 //We set the SM difference to zero
15482 double num = (trip_prod_pos_NP) - (trip_prod_neg_NP);
15483 double deno = (trip_prod_pos_Mad + trip_prod_pos_NP) + (trip_prod_neg_Mad + trip_prod_neg_NP);
15484
15485 double total = num/deno;
15486 return total;
15487
15488 }
15489 else{
15490
15491 double trip_prod_neg_NP = 0.4731751789769144*cHW + -0.2062173155393779*cHWtil + -0.0210420414673162*ctHIm +
15492 -0.0784772415015998*ctHRe + 0.0035049087021471*ctWIm + -1.1126408682479452*ctWRe;
15493 double trip_prod_pos_NP = 0.4764234225099984*cHW + 0.20722649465877*cHWtil + 0.0209093175097812*ctHIm +
15494 -0.078595795198671*ctHRe + -0.000362045416562*ctWIm + -1.150882604826262*ctWRe;
15495
15496
15497 //double num = (trip_prod_pos_Mad + trip_prod_pos_NP) - (trip_prod_neg_Mad + trip_prod_neg_NP);
15498 //double deno = (trip_prod_pos_Mad + trip_prod_pos_NP) + (trip_prod_neg_Mad + trip_prod_neg_NP);
15499
15500
15501 //We set the SM difference to zero
15502 double num = (trip_prod_pos_NP) - (trip_prod_neg_NP);
15503 double deno = (trip_prod_pos_Mad + trip_prod_pos_NP) + (trip_prod_neg_Mad + trip_prod_neg_NP);
15504
15505 double total = num/deno;
15506 return total;
15507
15508 }

16096sigma_250_bb_eLpR::sigma_250_bb_eLpR(const StandardModel& SM_i)
16097: ThObservable(SM_i),myNPSMEFT6dtopquark(static_cast<const NPSMEFT6dtopquark&> (SM_i))
16098{}
16099
16100double sigma_250_bb_eLpR::computeThValue()
16101{
16102 // double sigma_250_bb_eLpR_madgraph = 3290;//fb
16103 double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
16104 double C_phiQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();
16105 double C_phiQm = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQm();
16106 double C_phib = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phib();
16107 double C_bW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bW();
16108 double C_bB = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bB();
16109 double C_bZ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bZ();
16110 double C_ed = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
16111 double C_eq = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
16112 double C_ld = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
16113 double C_lqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();
16114 bool flag_LHC_WG_Basis=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_LHC_WG_Basis();
16115 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
16116
16117 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){
16118 if(flag_Quadratic){
16119 return 1000*((0.31*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.31*((C_phiQm+C_phiQ3)/0.998)+0.05*(C_phib/(0.998))+0.27*(C_bW)*(-1)*(C_bW)*(-1)+0.077*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)
16120 -0.25*(C_bW)*(-1)*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)+0.091*C_ed-0.064*C_eq+0.71*C_ld+3.77*C_lqP));
16121 }
16122 else{
16123 return 1000*(0.31*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.31*((C_phiQm+C_phiQ3)/0.998)+0.05*(C_phib/(0.998))
16124 +0.091*C_ed-0.064*C_eq+0.71*C_ld+3.77*C_lqP);
16125 }
16126 }
16127
16128 else{
16129 if(flag_Quadratic){
16130 return 1000*((0.31*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.31*(((C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3)+C_phiQ3)/0.998)+0.05*(C_phib/(0.998))+0.27*(C_bW)*(-1)*(C_bW)*(-1)+0.077*C_bB*(-1)*C_bB*(-1)
16131 -0.25*(C_bW)*(-1)*C_bB*(-1)+0.091*C_ed-0.064*C_eq+0.71*C_ld+3.77*C_lqP));
16132 }
16133 else{
16134 return 1000*(0.31*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.31*(((C_phiQ1-C_phiQ3)+C_phiQ3)/0.998)+0.05*(C_phib/(0.998))
16135 +0.091*C_ed-0.064*C_eq+0.71*C_ld+3.77*C_lqP);
16136 }
16137 }
16138}

16146double a_250_bb_eLpR::computeThValue()
16147{
16148 //double a_250_bb_eLpR_madgraph = 69.6; in percentage

16150 double C_phiQ3 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ3();
16151 double C_phiQ1 = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_phiQ1();

16781 bool flag_Quadratic=myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_flag_Quadratic();
16782 if(flag_LHC_WG_Basis){

16784 return 1000*(0.004*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.004*(((C_phiQm+C_phiQ3))/0.998)-0.006*(C_phib/(0.998))+0.014*C_bW*(-1)*C_bW*(-1)+0.29*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)

16786 }
16787 else{
16788 return 1000*(0.004*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.004*(((C_phiQm+C_phiQ3))/0.998)-0.006*(C_phib/(0.998))+1.55*C_ed-0.79*C_eq+0.046*C_ld+0.21*C_lqP);
16789 }
16790 }
16791 else{
16792 if(flag_Quadratic){
16793 return 1000*(0.004*(C_phiQ3/0.998)+0.004*((C_phiQ1)/0.998)-0.006*(C_phib/(0.998))+0.014*C_bW*(-1)*C_bW*(-1)+0.29*C_bB*(-1)*C_bB*(-1)

16795 }
16796 else{

16816 double C_bW = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bW();
16817 double C_bZ = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bZ();
16818 double C_bB = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_bB();
16819 double C_ed = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ed();
16820 double C_eq = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_eq();
16821 double C_ld = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_ld();
16822 double C_lqP = myNPSMEFT6dtopquark.getNPSMEFT6dtopquark_C_lqP();

16827 return (-6.8*(C_phiQ3/0.998)-6.8*(((C_phiQm+C_phiQ3))/0.998)-3.6*(C_phib/(0.998))-3.15*C_bW*(-1)*C_bW*(-1)-27.5*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)
16828 +0.44*C_bW*(-1)*((0.881533*C_bW-C_bZ)/0.47213)*(-1)+826*C_ed+1611*C_eq-120*C_ld+6.5*C_lqP)/100;
16829 }
16830 else{
16831 return (-6.8*(C_phiQ3/0.998)-6.8*(((C_phiQm+C_phiQ3))/0.998)-3.6*(C_phib/(0.998))+826*C_ed+1611*C_eq-120*C_ld+6.5*C_lqP)/100;
16832 }
16833 }
16834 else{
16835 if(flag_Quadratic){
16836 return (-6.8*(C_phiQ3/0.998)-6.8*((C_phiQ1)/0.998)-3.6*(C_phib/(0.998))-3.15*C_bW*(-1)*C_bW*(-1)-27.5*C_bB*(-1)*C_bB*(-1)
16837 +0.44*C_bW*(-1)*C_bB*(-1)+826*C_ed+1611*C_eq-120*C_ld+6.5*C_lqP)/100;
16838 }
16839 else{
16840 return (-6.8*(C_phiQ3/0.998)-6.8*((C_phiQ1)/0.998)-3.6*(C_phib/(0.998))+826*C_ed+1611*C_eq-120*C_ld+6.5*C_lqP)/100;
